    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3311960/extras/a2de6e5f17c9bf4e12e995692dfc2332.avif?t=1733875824\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3311960/extras_big/a2de6e5f17c9bf4e12e995692dfc2332.avif?t=1733875824 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你认为你准备好迎接终极挑战了吗？三步将杀解谜包专为渴望更复杂和精准战术的玩家设计。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3311960/extras/6323e236d16f559a1d82592f8cee3504.avif?t=1733875824\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3311960/extras_big/6323e236d16f559a1d82592f8cee3504.avif?t=1733875824 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过30个精心策划的谜题，你将被推向更深层次的思考、更敏锐的计算，力争在仅仅三步内找到将杀。</p>",
